This is only the fourth version of the Range
Rover in its 42 year history.

00:00:10.050 --> 00:00:12.220
And though the model become an icon during
that time.

00:00:12.220 --> 00:00:17.010
It has had its shortcomings and reliability
has always been a bit of an issue.

00:00:17.010 --> 00:00:21.300
So a whole heap of work needed to be done
to bring this British status symbol back up

00:00:21.300 --> 00:00:22.300
to scratch.

00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:25.119
Land rover has addressed most of these problem
areas.

00:00:25.119 --> 00:00:29.721
The brick like physique has been replaced
by a relatively sleek profile and the Range

00:00:29.721 --> 00:00:31.789
Rover has gone on a crash diet.

00:00:31.789 --> 00:00:36.860
It's the world's first SUV with an all aluminum
body.

