In fact this Range Rover is the first that's
light enough to be fitted with a V6 engine.

00:00:48.630 --> 00:00:53.540
The TD V6 is already used in the Range Rover
Sport and Discovery.

00:00:53.540 --> 00:00:55.510
That's done wonders for fuel economy and emissions.

00:00:55.510 --> 00:01:02.180
382 is down to 196 grams per kilometer and
claimed mpg is 37.7.

00:01:02.180 --> 00:01:05.300
This engine is paired with a smooth intelligent
8 speed automatic transmission.

00:01:05.300 --> 00:01:12.070
It can responses, depending on how heavy-footed
the driver is on the throttle.

00:01:12.070 --> 00:01:16.360
All models come with a new air suspension
system with continuously adaptive dampening

00:01:16.360 --> 00:01:20.710
that softens and stiffens the ride to suit
the road conditions.

00:01:20.710 --> 00:01:25.920
Inside, the driver sits more than nine centimeters
high than any other SUV.

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:29.200
And in the cabin, creature comforts abound.

00:01:29.200 --> 00:01:32.450
The last model was criticized for having a
lack of space in the back.

