00:01:38.729 --> 00:01:45.000
Boot space is improved too and we like the
convenience of the power upper and lower tailgates.

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:48.660
But the range rover is pricey to say the least.

00:01:48.660 --> 00:01:52.521
The cheapest model costs seventy thousand
pounds and the most expensive is almost a

00:01:52.521 --> 00:01:56.760
hundred thousand pounds and that's without
any optional extras.

00:01:56.760 --> 00:02:03.220
