Q7, BMW X5, and Porshe Cayenne all start around

00:02:03.220 --> 00:02:04.220
45 thousand.

00:02:04.220 --> 00:02:07.430
That's a whopping 25,000 pounds less.

00:02:07.430 --> 00:02:12.370
So is the Range Rover worth such a massive
price premium? despite all the great modern

00:02:12.370 --> 00:02:14.310
